wikipedia_page.main: Major Sir Cyril Fullard Entwistle, MC, QC (23 September 1887 – 9 July 1974) was a Liberal Party politician in the United Kingdom. He later defected to the Conservative Party. He was a Member of Parliament (MP) from 1918 to 1924 and from 1931 to 1945.

response: *Major Cyril Fullard Entwistle,  Member of Parliament for Bolton since October, 1931, and for South-West Hull, 1918 to 1924. For political and public services.
